\chapter{Resource Index}\label{ch:resources}

\paragraph{Overview.}
This chapter provides a comprehensive, annotated index of resources for further study. Resources are organised by category and annotated with difficulty level, relevance, and accessibility.

% ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
